Foreign Exchange







Back to Global Markets




We deliver both the global reach and local knowledge to help our clients manage currency risk exposure. 

Our strategic consultation, superior execution and excellence in FX research make us a full-service market maker and active liquidity provider in all major OTC currency markets. 
For our corporate clients, we provide hedging solutions, focusing on liability risk management and structured deposits. To better coordinate risk management activities, our teams are at the ready, around the world—New York, London, Tokyo, Hong Kong, Singapore and Shanghai. 






Annual World's Best FX Providers Awards: Best FX Research & Analysis - Forecasts (Mexican Peso)
            Global Finance Magazine
2016            



#1 Ranked Peso Forecaster
            Bloomberg
2015            












FX management to meet your needs

FX Spot
FX Forwards
FX Swaps
Non-Deliverable Forwards (NDF)
FX Options (including non-deliverable options)
Active G20 liquidity in spot, forward and option markets
Access to the Latin American, EMEA and Asian emerging markets
Global currency market research and analysis
Structured Products
 



A cutting-edge electronic trading platform
Our solution helps clients navigate the FX landscape from trade execution through settlement, with speed, efficiency and reliability in fast moving markets. It incorporates quality execution with a full suite of FX products such as Spot, Outrights, Rolls, Strips, Batch trades and more. The platform delivers liquidity through all of the major ECNs including FXall, Bloomberg and 360T. We can also deliver customized prices through the Swap-Execution-Facilities (SEFs) for both NDFs and FX options. 






