Futures + Options







Back to Global Markets




As a top tier Futures Commission Merchant, we provide clients with efficient and cost-effective access to global commodity and financial markets.  

Our comprehensive futures execution and clearing platform services both corporate and institutional clients including financial institutions, commercial hedgers, commodity trading advisors, hedge funds, money managers and pension funds. 
Here, you can access global futures positions and trade data with queries and reports designed to speed operations and support straight-through processing.
Log in to our futures portal 







A powerful execution and clearing platform








Electronic Execution

Industry leading technology backbone that provides reliable and efficient electronic trading
Technology support specialists available 24/6
Training and assistance throughout onboarding
Multiple e-trading platforms supported, including Trading Technologies, Bloomberg EMS, CQG 

Voice/High-touch Execution

Multilingual global execution desk available 24/6 with access to all supported exchanges
Market insight and expertise in handling electronic and open outcry transactions
Experienced floor execution coverage by CME and CBOT floor brokers

Clearing

Central clearing through a single platform to major global exchanges
Single currency margining and flexible collateral arrangements
Dedicated representatives to facilitate post-trade margining and client-specific requests
Web-deployed client portal with customized reporting and access to real-time and historical account data
Customized technology solutions as part of a straight-through processing option
Regulatory Registrations: Futures Commission Merchant, US Commodity Futures Trading Commission
Member, the National Futures Association. 
 



Exchange Access
Americas
CME, CBOT, NYMEX/COMEX, ICE Futures US, Montreal (TMX), MGEX, KCBT, CBOE (CFE), ICE Futures Canada, NYSE LIFFE US, BVMF, Nodal, Nasdaq Futures Exchange
Europe
Eurex, NYSE LIFFE, ICE Futures, Europe, LME, NYSE Euronext, ECX, EGX (Green Exchange)
Asia
TSE, TFX, TCE (TOCOM), OSE, HKFE, ASX (SFE), DME, SGX
Market Coverage
Financials
Financial Income/Interest Rates, Equity Indexes, Currencies
Commodities
Energy, Agricultural Complex, Metals, Emissions, Freight
 
View our Futures Disclosures 






