Industry Sectors







Back to Corporate + Investment Banking




We craft sector-specific solutions within the many industries that define the market in the Americas. 

Our deep expertise and custom solutions help our clients address the unique challenges and opportunities in every industry. 





IFR Magazine 2015 US Dollar Bond of the Year Award: Actavis’ $21B bond


Led $9.155B AT&T financing, one of the largest syndicated investment grade term loans ever placed in US (2015)


Lead arranger/underwriter on Dominion Resources acquisition of Questar (2016)














Consumer Retail
Financing and advisory services including M&A, divestitures, equity and debt financing, risk management and restructuring—for clients in apparel, education, e-commerce, food, household products, restaurants and supermarkets.

Financial Institutions
Financing and advisory services including M&A advisory, equity and debt financing, structured finance and risk management/hedging—for clients in banking, insurance, asset management, financial technology and specialty finance.

Financial Sponsors
We originate and structure the full suite of financial products for sponsor-backed and stand-alone non-investment grade corporates looking to access the institutional investor marketplace in the Americas. 
We offer acquisition finance solutions, including debt facilities, IPO and follow-on equity support, idea generation and M&A advisory—for private equity sponsors and corporate clients in manufacturing, chemicals, consumer, food and beverage, healthcare, packaging, print and publishing, media and entertainment, electronics, IT and business services, financial services, real estate and energy. 

Healthcare
Financing and advisory services including M&A, divestitures, equity and debt financing, risk management and restructuring—for clients in biotechnology, healthcare services, life sciences, medical technology and pharmaceuticals.

Industrial + Basic Materials
Investment banking services including M&A, divestitures, equity and debt financings, financial restructurings and risk management—for clients in aerospace and defense, automotive, building and construction, business services, capital goods, diversified industrials, transportation and infrastructure, paper, forest products and packaging.

Natural Resources + Energy
Corporate finance and investment banking services including M&A, leveraged buyouts, equity and debt financings, commodity hedging, joint venture restructurings and financial investments—for clients in the energy, chemicals, metals and mining and alternative energy fields, with comprehensive sub-sector coverage in exploration and production, downstream (refining and marketing), midstream (pipeline delivery) and oil services companies. 

Power + Utilities
Corporate finance and investment banking capabilities for M&A and cross-border transactions, equity and debt financings, commodity hedging, joint venture restructurings and financial investments—for power and utilities companies including power suppliers, public utilities, power generators and energy distribution networks.

Public Finance
Financing and municipal bond underwriting—for clients in infrastructure, state and local government, non-profit healthcare systems, higher education, public power and utilities, surface transportation agencies, airports and seaports, housing agencies and other public projects.

Real Estate
Financing and advisory services including M&A, IPOs and other equity offerings, leveraged financing, commercial-mortgage-backed securities, capital execution, loan syndication and securitization, and raising capital for projects—for clients in real estate investment trusts (REITs), public-sector entities, retail properties, hotels and golf courses, shopping centers, office buildings, industrial properties, multifamily properties, development projects, and casinos and gaming technology.

Technology/Media/Telecom
Financing and advisory services including M&A, IPOs and other equity offerings, debt underwriting, hybrid instruments, risk management, credit advisory and other financial services—for clients in electronics, software, internet, wireless and cable companies. 



